This species was described based on male and female specimens collected by J. Ogilvie at 
<collectingCountry id="F37C7652870AAA154315FBC6DE17AE6B" box="[1288,1399,1076,1102]" name="Barbados" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Barbados</collectingCountry>
